'''Crooked Tail''' was the nickname given to a [[Dulok/Legends|Dulok]] warrior by the [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] [[Teebo/Legends|Teebo]].

==Biography==
Crooked Tail was a large Dulok with blue-gray fur and a kinked tail. He belonged to King [[Vulgarr/Legends|Vulgarr's]] band. After Vulgarr and his Duloks had kidnapped the [[Wokling/Legends|woklings]] of [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]], Vulgarr decreed that they would feast on them. Crooked Tail disagreed and attacked Vulgarr with a short stone ax. One of Vulgarr's guards killed Crooked Tail with a blow to the head from a wooden club, ending the insurrection.

